file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Open API Sample
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /todos:
    get:
      description: "Returns all todo items"
      responses:
        200:
          description: "A list of todo items"
          schema:
            type: array
            items:
              type: object
              properties:
                id:
                  type: strin
                  format: uuid
                name:
                  type: string
